Commentary Text: Mustafizur to Ruturaj Gaikwad, SIX, what a way to get to your maiden IPL ton! Personal milestones aren't as important as team goals but you've got to say that the lad deserved this hundred. This was one heck of a batting masterclass and poetic justice that the innings ends with a Gaikwad sixer. Shuffles across early, gets the shortish length ball that he massacres over deep mid-wicket. The entire CSK dugout is on their feet

Commentary Text: Rahul Tewatia to Moeen Ali, wide, out Stumped!! Clever bowling from Tewatia! Must say Moeen made it easier too by charging down even before the bowler delivered the ball. Allowed Tewatia to adjust and adjust he did by firing it way wide outside off. Beyond the tramline and Moeen had no chance of reaching this. It's a wide but RR won't mind that, they have got a huge breakthrough here. Moeen Ali st Samson b Rahul Tewatia 21(17) [4s-1 6s-1]
